text.tspan: A planting simulation game aims to motivate users check the app frequently. When users
harvest something on the app, they can gain real stuff from the farm. We add weather
condition in the game in order to create empathy and connection with farmers
Buy and sell products of farm with pre-order. Pre-order not only allows the farm to share
the risk with consumers in other form but also meets the core value of users.
Users have to cook almost everything that buy from the farm so recipe is a useful
tool to attract users to come back after purchasing. We also mark out the ingredients
that users could buy directly from the Farm
User and can send message directly to QJ Farm, vice versa. It helps both side to
For users, there is a traditional shopping cart where they select items for eventual
purchase. For QJ Farm, theres order for they can check, accept and reject orders
